page.title: 13LIVING IN A l7th C.HOUSE 2
page.content: DININGROOM-fitted beige carpet;side- board;white oblong table;5 chairs with fabric covered seats;1 pine-panelled wall;others painted white;brown floral curtains;net curtains on short windows Open stairs to upper floor;brown carpetted.Central heating radiator. KITCHEN-White-painted wooden units. Fitted electric hob & oven,sink-unit, dish-washer,cooker-hood and extractor- fan.Free-standing washing-machine, clothes-dryer and fridge.Tiled walls, pine-clad walls and ceiling.Recessed fluorescent lights.Marble-patterned laminate work-surfaces.White and green vinyl(tile-effect) on floor.White and green floral curtains. BATHROOM-Cork floor.Walls tiled-mostly white,random patterned.Green bath, shower,fitted sink-unit and toilet. Pine cupboards;large mirror;heated light and towel rail;shaving mirror.
